platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When the sky falls, will you crumble—or will you stand tall? Test your mettle with Bluk, the game where all it takes to survive and save the world is your ability to manipulate—and defy—gravity. Using a simple touch, drag and release operation, you will propel a block through the stratosphere without falling off the edge of a shifting world, making for consistently slick and thrilling gameplay. We love the endless challenge and the minimalist landscape of this poetic, physics-based platformer from Kerala indie developer Pixel Ape Studios.
